      • tryMix

        public boolean tryMix()
        Attempt to refill the can from the contents of the can's inventory. The mixer needs to find a milk bucket and at least one dye. If mixing is successful, the bucket is replaced with an empty bucket and dye is removed, and the method returns true.
        Returns:
        true if mixing was successful, false otherwise
